      <p>1. Better Inspired Lifestyle </p>
      <p>2. More tasty and Healthy. Organic food is great antioxidant, which   helps neutralize free radicals that are thought to contribute to ageing   and cancer. </p>
      <p>3. Buying Organic products shows that you are caring towards your family and the Mother Earth </p>
      <p>4. Fashionable and stylish organic textile ranges are now available   for you to choose from, Organic cotton cloths are highly recommended for   the kids and somebody suffering for skin allergies. </p>
      <p>5. There was a time when Organic products used to be very costly, but   now things are changing. Thanks to you all, with growing demands for   the organic products, the prices are also almost at par with the   conventional products. </p>
      <p>6. All certified Organic Products passes the strict guidelines and   follow Fair Trade Practices. So, you can be assure of better quality   products with no adulteration and  use of chemical. </p>
      <p>7. Great Surprises with new range of organic products are being introduced almost everyday. </p>
